{"type": "article", "id": 7012, "title": "Botanical Life 创意台历", "description": "", "date": "2015-03-03T07:55:34Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 19, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234248gZJXHMouc4i3jzIC.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"white-space:normal;\">来自日本的 Good Morning 公司带来的这款台历核心理念是“少即使多”。这些台历每两个月作为一页出现。每页如同一张贺卡，当打开台历，中间的树木，树叶等形状立体展现在人们面前。通过这一套台历，Good Morning 公司意在向全世界宣告起环保理念。相信这也是iF设计大奖中意他们的重要原因。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"white-space:normal;\">\r\n\t<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234247hvcPXJwAKFbCEatU.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:696px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66851852\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n\t</p>\r\n\t<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234248KFN45ojQukzL6cMU.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:696px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66851852\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n\t</p>\r\n<br>\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}